1️⃣ 👑 Admin

👉 System controller

Role:
Manage all users (students & recruiters)
Approve/reject portfolios
Remove harmful content
Monitor platform activity
Manage rankings (optional control)

💡 Think: Owner of the platform

2️⃣ 👨‍💻 Student / Developer

👉 Main content creators

Role:
Register & login
Upload portfolio (ZIP)
Get live portfolio link
Manage their profile (skills, bio, resume)
Track views / ranking

💡 Think: People who showcase their work

3️⃣ 💼 Recruiter

👉 Talent seekers

Role:
Browse student profiles
View portfolios
Filter/search candidates
Contact students
Use ranking system to find top talent

💡 Think: Companies / HR / interviewers

4️⃣ 🌐 Guest User (Public Visitor)

👉 No login required

Role:
View portfolios
Explore top students
Basic browsing

⚠️ Limited access:

No upload
No advanced filters
No messaging

💡 Think: First-time visitor / casual recruiter

🧠 Final Structure (Simple View)
            Admin
              |
   ------------------------
   |          |           |
Student   Recruiter     Guest
